    "type": "faq",
    "data": {
            "title": "FAQ",
            "subtitle": "Travelers Ask",
            "items": [{
                    "question": "Are all these hotels in the Netherlands (Utrecht) suitable for big dogs?",
                    "answer": "Not necessarily  but finding the right one is easy. Just use the “Pets” filter on our website and select “From 10-15kg pet allowed”. We’ll show you only the hotels that clearly allow big dogs, so you can book with confidence."
            }, {
                    "question": "Do I need to pay extra for my small dog more than 10 kg to stay in the Netherlands (Utrecht)?",
                    "answer": "Some hotels may charge a pet fee, but many don’t. By using our “Pet Fee” filter, you can easily find hotels that either don’t charge a fee or have a pet fee less than €20 per night. This way, you avoid surprises and book the best stay for you and your dog."
            }, {
                    "question": "Are there nearby parks or walking areas for small dogs more than 10 kg in Utrecht?",
                    "answer": "Yes, and to make it even easier, you can use the “Pet walking area nearby” filter in the “Pets” section on our website. It helps you find hotels located close to dog-friendly parks and green zones, perfect for short walks with your small dog."
            }, {
                    "question": "Do I need to show my dog's vaccination records?",
                    "answer": "Some hotels may require vaccination records, but many don’t. You can use our “No pet vaccination required” filter in the “Pets” section to find hotels that don’t ask for this. However, we still recommend bringing your dog’s vaccination documents when traveling just in case."
            }, {
                    "question": "Is there a weight limit for my big dog more than 10kg?",
                    "answer": "Some hotels do set weight limits, but you can easily find the right options using our filters. Just select “No pet weight limit” in the “Pets” section on our website to see hotels that welcome big dogs without strict restrictions."
            }, {
                    "question": "What should I bring for my big dog more than 10kg?",
                    "answer": "Each hotel card on our website shows what's included in the room. To find the most pet-ready stays faster, use our filters like “Towels for pets”, “Additional pet services”, or “Toys for pets” in the “Pets” section during your search."
            }]
    }
}

